freetype-infinality (2.4.8-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Modify Debian freetype package to package the Infinality patch set
  * debian/control
    - Remove docs and demos
    - Remove dev package
  * debian/rules
    - Remove docs and demos
    - Remove explicit patch sections
    - Disable treating warnings as errors (-Werror)
    - Remove version lines
    - Remove files that don't get installed from debian/tmp (commented)
  * debian/source/format
    - Created this file so that the Quilt patches work
  * debian/patches/freetype-2.1.7-backwards.compat.patch
    - Refreshed to use the standard "-p1" patching
  * debian/README.Source
    - Removed (content doesn't apply)
  * debian/freetype-config.man.sgml
    - Removed (no need for man page for a non-installed binary)
  * Added lintian overrides (commented in respective files)
  * Remove patches for freetype demos
  * Remove debian patch for enabling subpixel rendering
  * Reorganize structure since there's only one source package now
  * Moved original freetype changelog to debian/changelog.freetype
    - Works around lintian version checks (same as previous changelog version
